WHO   — Darwi Odrade — the Mother Superior who let herself feel
WHAT  — The Mother Superior of the Bene Gesserit, of the old Atreides line, who rose to lead the Sisterhood.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: The Bene Gesserit Sisterhood — the late saga, the war with the Honored Matres  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — She taught the Bene Gesserit, at last, how to change — to feel the love the Sisterhood forbids.
HOW   — She led the order through its war with the Honored Matres, gambling its survival on a plan to absorb rather than destroy the enemy.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The Sisterhood learning, at last, how to change.

